	-----------------------------------------------

	to run the server (TomCat):
	goto "http://localhost:8088/dynamicWeb/" for DynamicWeb project
	goto "http://localhost:8088/dynamicWebTesting/" for DynamicWebTesting project
	goto "http://localhost:8088/eZoo/" for eZoo project
	
	-----------------
	
	Postgres DATABASE
		
	posgres pw: postgresLovely1
	port: 5432
	dataabse: postgres
	url: jdbc:postgresql://localhost:5432/postgres
	username: postgres
	
	How to open postgres pgAdmin:
	- launch from start and find pgAdmin
	- or go to url "http://127.0.0.1:62107/browser/"
	
	To create database, go to pgAdmin from menu , right click on Database -> new 
	To create or run sql query, select on the database you want and select Tool -> query tool from menu bar
	
	
	
	
